[[!ftemplate id=tool]]

AbiWord is a word processor. It is written using Gtk+3 and provides an
embeddable widget called [[AbiWidget|http://www.abisource.com/wiki/AbiWidget]]
that can be loaded into other Gtk+3 applications.
